d to fend off zombies with firearms for self-preservation and successfully reach the designated endpoint in order to achieve successful escape. The immediate infection of all human players by zombies results in victory.", "short_description": "The first VR Biochemical frenzy online battle in history, Multiplayer shooter in VR with zombies escape, officially opened"}]}, "developer_name": "Holo", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://vrdanceyinsi.webnode.page/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Holoren", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://renrenren.webnode.page/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "3744040075834813"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["CO_OP", "MULTI_USER"], "id": "7850424621689264"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "26781769688076898"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "26781769688076898"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1719537818, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "26781769688076898"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8974211885977193", "version": "0.3.5"}, "id": "7552059071571728", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7821371324594594", "is_concept": false,